Package org.infernalstudios.config.annotation

package org.infernalstudios.config.annotation
  • Annotation Interfaces Summary
    Annotation Interface
    Description
    AutoSerializable
    Tells the config builder to attempt to automatically serialize and deserialize all the classes public fields.
    Category
    Specifies the category of all @Configurable fields.
    Configurable
    Specifies that this field is now configurable by the config system.
    DoubleRange
    Specifies the bounds for a @Configurable field.
    FloatRange
    Specifies the bounds for a @Configurable field.
    IntegerRange
    Specifies the bounds for a @Configurable field.
    ListValue
    Specifies that the field is a List field with elements that require special (de)serialization handlers.
